content_html: The funeral procession for the Gyanjya Martyrs has begun in Kathmandu. The bodies of ten people who lost their lives during the Gyanjya Martyrs movement on September 9 have been taken from the Teaching Hospital to Pashupati Aryaghat. Their bodies are being carried in a formal funeral procession.
